759
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,800
- Just take it.
- You just…

760
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,159
- Come on.
- Alright.

761
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:27,679
Take it.
Give it to me.

762
00:39:28,519 --> 00:39:29,119
Ma'am,

763
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,280
