767
00:39:34,519 --> 00:39:35,360
Thank you so much.
Alright, I'll leave you to it.

768
00:39:37,119 --> 00:39:37,519
Okay.
- Take care.
- I'll walk you out.

769
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:39,519
Alright.

770
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:40,599
We're heading off.

771
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:42,719
It's fine.

772
