what I just said.

776
00:39:48,719 --> 00:39:49,440
I'll head over there.
I'll head over there.

777
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:52,280
Where are you going? Sit down.

778
00:39:52,639 --> 00:39:53,320
You're really…
Be seated.

779
00:40:01,239 --> 00:40:01,960
[Mrs. Zhao]

780
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,239
