[figure out the puzzle of marriage.]

786
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:16,639
[I just couldn't help wondering]

787
00:40:17,559 --> 00:40:18,800
[how did two people who can't]

788
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:19,599
[even talk anymore]

789
00:40:20,079 --> 00:40:20,639
[end up]

790
00:40:20,639 --> 00:40:22,039
[together in the first place?]

791
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,639
[At the beginning,]

792
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,639
I just thought

793
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,519
