802
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:48,920
One sentence from him can knock you flat

803
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:49,960
and leave you reeling for hours!

804
00:40:51,079 --> 00:40:51,840
Ms. Ruan,

805
00:40:52,639 --> 00:40:54,679
