827
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,079
[be exactly]

828
00:41:37,079 --> 00:41:38,639
[what you dislike.]

829
00:41:39,599 --> 00:41:40,880
[So you need to figure out]

830
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,559
[what matters most]

831
00:41:42,559 --> 00:41:43,599
[to you.]

832
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:46,400
