860
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:56,920
I'm not trying to fool you.

861
00:42:58,079 --> 00:42:59,000
I was just wondering,

862
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:00,840
at your age,

863
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:02,199
