873
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:21,119
from now on?

874
00:43:23,039 --> 00:43:23,960
Then do you know

875
00:43:24,360 --> 00:43:25,599
my parents

876
00:43:25,960 --> 00:43:26,920
are divorced too?

877
00:43:28,280 --> 00:43:29,000
[They split up]

878
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,639
[when I was in high school.]

879
00:43:31,719 --> 00:43:32,400
[After that,]

880
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:35,000
[I went abroad with my dad.]

881
00:43:36,119 --> 00:43:37,119
[And I never really had]

882
00:43:37,880 --> 00:43:39,000
[my mom]

883
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:40,760
[or my sister around again.]

884
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:42,360
[But Huan, look at me,]

885
00:43:43,280 --> 00:43:43,840
[I'm doing]

886
00:43:43,840 --> 00:43:44,960
[just fine, right?]

887
00:43:45,800 --> 00:43:48,599
[But were you]

888
00:43:48,599 --> 00:43:49,440
[not sad back then?]

889
00:43:50,679 --> 00:43:51,679
[Of course I was]
[sad back then.]

890
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,199
But later I realized,

891
00:43:56,400 --> 00:43:58,840
if they stayed together

892
00:43:59,360 --> 00:44:00,840
just for me and my sister,

893
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:02,039
forcing it against their will,

894
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:04,519
I might have felt

895
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:05,639
even worse.

896
00:44:06,800 --> 00:44:07,760
Like now,

897
00:44:08,719 --> 00:44:10,239
if your parents

898
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,639
aren't happy together,

899
00:44:12,599 --> 00:44:13,920
can you really be happy?

900
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:15,639
Hearing them argue every day

901
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:17,320
makes me unhappy too.

902
00:44:17,800 --> 00:44:18,599
Exactly.

903
00:44:19,079 --> 00:44:20,159
If staying together

904
00:44:20,159 --> 00:44:21,599
only leads to constant fights,

905
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:23,599
then separation

906
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:24,320
might be

907
00:44:24,320 --> 00:44:25,519
a way forward.

908
00:44:26,599 --> 00:44:27,480
We're all

909
00:44:28,199 --> 00:44:29,039
born as
independent individuals.

910
00:44:30,639 --> 00:44:31,159
Parents don't

911
00:44:31,159 --> 00:44:32,599
have to stay together,

912
00:44:33,159 --> 00:44:33,719
and we don't

913
00:44:33,719 --> 00:44:34,800
have to be

914
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:35,840
bound to them either.

915
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:37,199
We each have

916
00:44:37,199 --> 00:44:38,239
our own lives to live.

917
00:44:39,280 --> 00:44:40,880
So whether they stay together

918
00:44:41,079 --> 00:44:41,840
or not,

919
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:43,280
it won't affect

920
00:44:43,559 --> 00:44:45,119
you growing up into yourself

921
00:44:45,239 --> 00:44:46,639
and living your own life.

922
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:48,400
I get it, bro.

923
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:50,199
If they're

924
00:44:50,199 --> 00:44:51,719
happier apart,

925
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:53,920
I'll support them.

926
00:44:54,440 --> 00:44:55,880
Even if they split up,

927
00:44:56,320 --> 00:44:58,079
I'm still me, right?

928
00:44:59,719 --> 00:45:00,400
Of course.

929
00:45:00,920 --> 00:45:02,159
You're still you.

930
00:45:03,639 --> 00:45:04,280
Huan,

931
00:45:05,239 --> 00:45:06,199
why did you run out

932
00:45:06,199 --> 00:45:07,280
without saying a word?

933
00:45:07,280 --> 00:45:07,880
Do you know how worried
I was?

934
00:45:09,320 --> 00:45:11,039
Mr. Xu, I'm sorry.

935
00:45:11,039 --> 00:45:11,960
We've caused you trouble.
It's fine, Mrs. Zhao.

936
00:45:13,760 --> 00:45:14,679
Go home with your mom for now.

937
00:45:15,039 --> 00:45:16,079
And remember

938
00:45:16,079 --> 00:45:17,159
what I just told you.

939
00:45:17,639 --> 00:45:18,320
Thank you, bro,
see you.

940
00:45:39,679 --> 00:45:41,840
Wanna go for a walk?

941
00:46:06,559 --> 00:46:08,280
The moon looks so full tonight,

942
00:46:08,519 --> 00:46:09,559
and so bright.

943
00:46:10,519 --> 00:46:11,400
Why is that?

944
00:46:15,199 --> 00:46:16,000
A shooting star!

945
00:46:16,280 --> 00:46:17,480
Quick, make a wish!

946
00:46:17,880 --> 00:46:18,719
So fast!

947
00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:19,360
I…

948
00:46:25,199 --> 00:46:28,119
[Hope I'll get another chance]

949
00:46:28,880 --> 00:46:29,800
[to see Huaisong.]

950
00:46:50,920 --> 00:46:53,480
[Hope we can meet again someday,]

951
00:46:54,719 --> 00:46:55,320
[Yu.]
